| `bookId` | String | âœ… Yes | Identifies which book to display (essential for page functionality) |
| `fromCategory` | String | âŒ No | Tracks which category user came from (for analytics or context) |
| `highlightSection` | String | âŒ No | Section to highlight on page load (e.g., "reviews", "similar-books") |

