## ğŸ“ Notes for Future Reference

### Quick Navigation Reference

**Action Checklist:**
```
Forward Navigation:
âœ… Use Navigate To
âœ… Replace OFF (unless login/auth)
âœ… Slide Left (hierarchical)
âœ… Pass parameters from variables

Modal Navigation:
âœ… Use Navigate To
âœ… Replace OFF
âœ… Slide Up (temporary context)

Back Navigation:
âœ… Use Navigate Back
âœ… No configuration needed
âœ… Automatic transition reversal

Login/Auth:
âœ… Navigate To with Replace ON
âœ… Prevents back to login screen
```

### Route Design Patterns

**Path Parameters (Required):**
```
/resource/{id}
Example: /book/{bookId}
Use: Resource identifiers
```

**Query Parameters (Optional):**
```
/resource?param=value
Example: /books?category=fiction
Use: Filters, sorts, optional context
```

### Common Mistakes to Avoid

âŒ Using Slide Up for hierarchical navigation  
âŒ Forgetting to set Replace Route for login flows  
âŒ Making optional parameters required  
âŒ Inconsistent transition patterns  
âŒ Not passing required parameters  

âœ… Consistent transitions for similar navigation types  
âœ… Replace Route only for special flows  
âœ… Clear required vs optional distinction  
âœ… Meaningful, shareable URLs  
âœ… Platform-consistent patterns
